resources.string: We just need your registered Email Id to sent you password reset instructions.

"1) This app is only for those students who are studying in colleges affiliated by Rajasthan Technical University (RTU).

2) This app is only for Bachelor of technology (B.Tech) students.

3) If there is any query related to this app or the content in this app then there is a mail option avaliable below.

 4) If you feel that paper of any year and of any subject is missing please feel free to mail us.

Thanks for using this app"

"This app was developed by Aayush , as he came to know about the problems faced by students at the time of examination .The problem like not getting the useful content like previous years papers and latest syllabus of all the subject and of all branches.\nThis app is the soluction for all problems like these.\n"
